# Helm dependency artefacts are regenerated by
#   helm dependency update charts/keyrock
# and should not be tracked in git. The `common` library chart is
# consumed via a local `file://../common` dependency — the resolved
# subchart is packaged at install / publish time. The `**` globs also
# cover nested fixture charts (e.g. charts/common/tests).
charts/**/Chart.lock
charts/**/charts/

# Locally-installed tools (e.g. kubeconform, helm-docs) fetched by
# developers running ./eval.sh without a system-wide install.
bin/
